Detailed Description

cvmx_tra::_int_status

TRA_INT_STATUS = Trace Buffer Interrupt Status

Description:

Notes: During a CSR write to this register, the write data is used as a mask to clear the selected status bits (status'[3:0] = status[3:0] & ~write_data[3:0]).
